        <p MadCap:conditions="TargetEditor.EPUB,TargetEditor.HTML5,TargetEditor.HTMLHelp,TargetEditor.PDF,TargetEditor.Print,TargetEditor.Web,TargetEditor.WebHelp,TargetEditor.WebHelpAIR,TargetEditor.WebHelpMobile,TargetEditor.WebHelpPlus,TargetEditor.Word,TargetEditor.XHTML,TargetEditor.XPS,TargetEditor.EclipseHelp"><span class="bold">Right-to-Left:&#160;</span>This group box will only become active if a RTL&#160;language is selected above (Arabic, Hebrew, Persian, Urdu, Yiddish). These options were created to accommodate projects which may have been translated from a LTR&#160;language to a RTL&#160;language.</p>
