            <li MadCap:conditions="TargetEditor.Word,TargetEditor.PDF,TargetEditor.XPS,TargetEditor.XHTML"><span class="bold">Invert Page Layouts: </span>During compile, inverts page layouts from "right"&#160;to "left"&#160;and vice versa. It is important to note that this option will not simply swap out a Left page for a Right page, or a First Left for a First Right. If a chapter is set to begin on a First Right page and this option is enabled, Flare will still use the First Right page, but it will create a mirrored version of it and shift it to the right.</li>
